    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将考虑将宗教豁免纳入试管受精保险范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/trump-says-he-would-consider-religious-exemptions-to-ivf-care</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将考虑宗教豁免，以履行其竞选承诺，承担体外受精的费用，这是对一些反对生育手术的保守派基督教支持者做出的让步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/trump-says-he-would-consider-religious-exemptions-to-ivf-care</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 03:11:22 GMT</pubDate>
